  "root_text": {
    "an8.75:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8.75 ",
    "an8.75:0.2": "8. Yamakavagga ",
    "an8.75:0.3": "Paṭhamasampadāsutta ",
    "an8.75:1.1": "“Aṭṭhimā, bhikkhave, sampadā. ",
    "an8.75:1.2": "Katamā aṭṭha? ",
    "an8.75:1.3": "Uṭṭhānasampadā, ārakkhasampadā, kalyāṇamittatā, samajīvitā, saddhāsampadā, sīlasampadā, cāgasampadā, paññāsampadā—",
    "an8.75:1.4": "imā kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha sampadāti. ",
    "an8.75:2.1": "Uṭṭhātā kammadheyyesu, ",
    "an8.75:2.2": "appamatto vidhānavā; ",
    "an8.75:2.3": "Samaṁ kappeti jīvikaṁ, ",
    "an8.75:2.4": "sambhataṁ anurakkhati. ",
    "an8.75:3.1": "Saddho sīlena sampanno, ",
    "an8.75:3.2": "vadaññū vītamaccharo; ",
    "an8.75:3.3": "Niccaṁ maggaṁ visodheti, ",
    "an8.75:3.4": "sotthānaṁ samparāyikaṁ. ",
    "an8.75:4.1": "Iccete aṭṭha dhammā ca, ",
    "an8.75:4.2": "saddhassa gharamesino; ",
    "an8.75:4.3": "Akkhātā saccanāmena, ",
    "an8.75:4.4": "ubhayattha sukhāvahā. ",
    "an8.75:5.1": "Diṭṭhadhammahitatthāya, ",
    "an8.75:5.2": "samparāyasukhāya ca; ",
    "an8.75:5.3": "Evametaṁ gahaṭṭhānaṁ, ",
    "an8.75:5.4": "cāgo puññaṁ pavaḍḍhatī”ti. ",
    "an8.75:5.5": "Pañcamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an8.75:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 8.75 ",
    "an8.75:0.2": "8. Pairs ",
    "an8.75:0.3": "Accomplishments (1st) ",
    "an8.75:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these eight accomplishments. ",
    "an8.75:1.2": "What eight? ",
    "an8.75:1.3": "Accomplishment in initiative, protection, good friendship, and balanced finances. And accomplishment in faith, ethics, generosity, and wisdom. ",
    "an8.75:1.4": "These are the eight accomplishments. ",
    "an8.75:2.1": "They’re enterprising in the workplace, ",
    "an8.75:2.2": "diligent in managing things, ",
    "an8.75:2.3": "they balance their finances, ",
    "an8.75:2.4": "and preserve their wealth. ",
    "an8.75:3.1": "Faithful, accomplished in ethics, ",
    "an8.75:3.2": "bountiful, rid of stinginess, ",
    "an8.75:3.3": "they always purify the path ",
    "an8.75:3.4": "to well-being in lives to come. ",
    "an8.75:4.1": "And so these eight qualities ",
    "an8.75:4.2": "of a faithful householder of discernment ",
    "an8.75:4.3": "are declared by the one who is truly named ",
    "an8.75:4.4": "to lead to happiness in both spheres, ",
    "an8.75:5.1": "welfare and benefit in this life, ",
    "an8.75:5.2": "and happiness in lives to come. ",
    "an8.75:5.3": "This is how, for a householder, ",
    "an8.75:5.4": "merit grows by generosity.” "
  },
